支持</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">喂大佬呀, 無人做主持你熱狗撚有課金分成咩？<br />\n<br />\n你黃洋達係咪一條友做晒24小時節目佢呀?<br />\n<br />\n依家講到主持係受熱狗恩惠咁, 你熱狗無拆返佣既?<br />\n根本只係互利相惠之嘛！<br />\n<br />\n同共匪講東江水係恩惠有乜分別?<br />\n<br />\n本土大台DNA根深蒂固<br />\n熱狗以為自己係本土CCTVB大台？</span></span>"},{"pid":"c44c5a8262bb9e73b9fa06ca8d1f6bbad67aeeac","tid":189220,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有嗰一輪網絡23條 鍵盤戰線明顯比熱血時報紅囉<br />\n做乜學晒黃洋達黃毓民班冚家剷 明明偷人光環都倒轉來講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係! 人地反網絡23條, 又擺街站, 又上論壇, 又上電視, 又上立法會<br />\n<br />\n熱普賤都唔知去撚左邊, 好意思搶功勞? 真係厚顏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/ftp/News/20160702/HK/_02GK017_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Ftor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20160702%2FHK%2F_02GK017_.jpg&h=ef3a3ac0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74280c0f7c673808108db873cb2de9fac382ac9c","tid":189220,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有嗰一輪網絡23條 鍵盤戰線明顯比熱血時報紅囉<br />\n做乜學晒黃洋達黃毓民班冚家剷 明明偷人光環都倒轉來講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係! 人地反網絡23條, 又擺街站, 又上論壇, 又上電視, 又上立法會<br />\n<br />\n熱普賤都唔知去撚左邊, 好意思搶功勞? 真係厚顏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/ftp/News/20160702/HK/_02GK017_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Ftor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20160702%2FHK%2F_02GK017_.jpg&h=ef3a3ac0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/g7fqyyprl/13612285_287710511581702_2462920989627444613_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fg7fqyyprl%2F13612285_287710511581702_2462920989627444613_n.jpg&h=df69afe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2282038c1ffd33be36aa392e7b8635e8a7f1cad8","tid":189220,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>